OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FA mother from Somerset says parents
OL,7,Fwho have children with special
OL,8,Feducational needs and disabilities are
OL,9,Fdesperate for help.
OL,11,FAmy Barton told ITV News she was
OL,12,Fforced to remortgage her home to pay
OL,13,Ffor solicitors to fight for her son's
OL,14,Fsupport.
OL,16,FShe says many parents of children with
OL,17,FSEND are being left 'financially and
OL,18,Femotionally drained' from the burden
OL,19,Fof battling to get the help they need.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,F'It drains you completely, you're
OL,7,Fconstantly fighting just to get your
OL,8,Fchild what they need'
OL,10,FToday the government has announced its
OL,11,Fwidely anticipated, and long-delayed,
OL,12,FSchools White Paper after months of
OL,13,Fspeculation and leaks.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FThe government hopes the #4 billion
OL,7,Fpackage will help make mainstream
OL,8,Fschools more inclusive, including a
OL,9,F#1.6 billion 'inclusive mainstream
OL,10,Ffund' for early years, schools and
OL,11,Fcolleges, and #1.8 billion to place
OL,12,Fspecialist staff such as SEND teachers
OL,13,Fand speech therapists in every area.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
