OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,7,Fconfirmed that Education, Health and
OL,8,FCare Plans (EHCPs) will be retained
OL,9,Ffor children with the most complex
OL,10,Fneeds, while a new tiered system of
OL,11,FIndividual Support Plans (ISPs) will
OL,12,Fbe introduced for those with less
OL,13,Fsevere needs, with no diagnosis
OL,14,Frequired to access
OL,15,Fthem.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FAmy Barton's son Archie is 11 and has
OL,7,Fautism. Amy says the family was forced
OL,8,Fto make the difficult decision to
OL,9,Fremortgage her home to pay for
OL,10,Fsolicitors just to fight for the
OL,11,Fsupport she says her son was legally
OL,12,Fentitled to.
OL,14,FAt Archie's mainstream primary school
OL,15,Fhe was bullied and his mental health
OL,16,Fdeteriorated to a worrying degree, Amy
OL,17,Ftold ITV News.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,F"He'd pull his hair out and pull his
OL,7,Feyebrows out. To hear your child has a
OL,8,Fform of self-harm, it's one of the
OL,9,Fhardest things to hear from a
OL,10,Fprofessional.
OL,12,F"Your biggest fear becomes how will
OL,13,Fthat escalate, what will happen in the
OL,14,Ffuture, so that was my driver to
OL,15,Fensure he had the right support."
OL,17,FIt was at this point that Amy and her
OL,18,Fhusband remortgaged their home, so
OL,19,Fthey could try and get Archie the help
OL,20,Fhe needed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FShe says it cost them #20,000 in in
OL,7,Fprivate assessments and solicitor fees
OL,8,Fto get the EHCP Archie needed to make
OL,9,Fsure he was supported properly at the
OL,10,Fright school.
OL,12,FThat didn't just come at a financial
OL,13,Fcost, but an emotional one too.
OL,15,F"It's the most overwhelming thing
OL,16,Fwe've had to deal with as parents. It
OL,17,Fbroke me, I had to seek counselling,
OL,18,Fthe emotional and mental toll it has
OL,19,Fon people is not insignificant. I'm
OL,20,Fpart of multiple support groups and
OL,21,Fpeople are just desperate."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FHannah McCormack a mother from
OL,7,FNewquay, who has three children who
OL,8,Fneed varying levels of SEND provision,
OL,9,Fsays she has also been exhausted by
OL,10,Fthe process of trying to get them
OL,11,Fsupport.
OL,13,F"Some days, the children are in bed
OL,14,Fand I cry, but I think that's what
OL,15,Flacking in Cornwall, that support for
OL,16,Fparents with children with additional
OL,17,Fneeds."
OL,19,FHannah's two older children have been
OL,20,Fin mainstream education, but she says
OL,21,Fthe struggle has been relentless.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FShe took her son out of school in the
OL,7,Fmonths before his GCSEs because he
OL,8,F'couldn't cope'.
OL,10,FHer middle daughter is now preparing
OL,11,Ffor the move to mainstream secondary
OL,12,Fschool, but Hannah told ITV News she
OL,13,Fnow dreads what lies ahead.
OL,15,F"There are large classrooms, sometimes
OL,16,Fover 30 children, with one teacher,
OL,17,Fthere's been budget cuts so for one
OL,18,Fteacher to provide individualised
OL,19,Flearning to 30-plus students is almost
OL,20,Fimpossible."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FHannah's youngest daughter, Sienna
OL,7,FRose, attends a specialist school, and
OL,8,Fshe says the difference has been
OL,9,Ftransformative.
OL,11,FBefore Sienna Rose started school, she
OL,12,Fwas non-verbal and unresponsive.
OL,14,F"We didn't think Sienna Rose would
OL,15,Fwalk or talk, she was non-verbal, she
OL,16,Fwouldn't respond to us calling her
OL,17,Fname, however having the right
OL,18,Feducational setting for her she has
OL,19,Fcome leaps and bounds and it's laid
OL,20,Fthat foundation for her personal,
OL,21,Fsocial and emotional development.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,F"It's about recognising every child is
OL,7,Fdifferent."
OL,9,FKelly, a mother from Bath, who has
OL,10,Fthree neurodiverse children of her
OL,11,Fown, has fought the same battles and
OL,12,Fnavigated the same gruelling processes
OL,13,Fthat Amy and Hannah describe.
OL,15,FNow, having come out the other side,
OL,16,Fshe uses that experience to help other
OL,17,Fparents find their way through the
OL,18,Fsystem.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FShe said: "For a lot of families this
OL,7,Fis their first time in the SEND space
OL,8,Fand it is a massive learning curve.
OL,10,F"You get these enormous reports you
OL,11,Fdon't understand, there's different
OL,12,Facronyms and different routes and if
OL,13,Fyou don't know what you're doing it
OL,14,Fcan be a really hard road to take.
OL,16,F"A lot of people just stop and say
OL,17,Fit's too hard to understand, I'm tired
OL,18,Fof fighting, I can't do it anymore and
OL,19,Fif you have to fight for multiple
OL,20,Fchildren it's exhausting."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FWhat has been announced?
OL,8,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,9,Fpromised education, health and care
OL,10,Fplans (EHCPs), a legal document
OL,11,Fsetting out the support children with
OL,12,FSEND are entitled to, will stay "for
OL,13,Fchildren with the most complex needs
OL,14,Fwill stay".
OL,16,FMainstream schools will receive direct
OL,17,Ffunding to support SEND children as
OL,18,Fpart of a #4 billion package, to make
OL,19,Fthe system more inclusive, including
OL,20,Finvestment in training for adaptive
OL,21,Fteaching styles.
OL,26,@tD@aOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FSome #1.6 billion over three years
OL,7,Fwill be provided to early years,
OL,8,Fschools, and colleges through an
OL,9,F"inclusive mainstream fund".
OL,11,FWhile another #1.8 billion over the
OL,12,Fsame period will go towards creating
OL,13,Fan "experts at hand" service, made up
OL,14,Fof specialists such as SEND teachers
OL,15,Fand speech and language therapists in
OL,16,Fevery area.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@[O]uD@DOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FThe White Paper sets out to change the
OL,7,Fcurrent legal rights of children with
OL,8,Fless severe needs and instead
OL,9,Festablish a new tiered structure for
OL,10,Fsupporting SEND children, based on the
OL,11,Flevel of their need.
OL,13,FThe proportion of children with SEND
OL,14,Fon the current highest level of school
OL,15,Fsupport is projected to start falling
OL,16,Feach year from the end of the decade.
OL,18,FMaking a speech at a school in the
OL,19,FEast Midlands, Phillipson said:
OL,20,F"Forget the misinformation you might
OL,21,Fhave heard.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,F"EHCPs for children with the most
OL,7,Fcomplex needs will stay, guided by
OL,8,Fnationally defined and evidence-based
OL,9,Fspecialist provision packages."
OL,11,FWhat are the changes to EHCPs?
OL,13,FCurrently, parents face long waits to
OL,14,Faccess support for their children and
OL,15,Fthe Department for Education (DfE)
OL,16,Fsaid demand for EHCPs has more than
OL,17,Fdoubled since 2014.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FAround one in eight children with SEND
OL,7,Fwho currently have the highest support
OL,8,Fwill transition to new plans between
OL,9,F2030 and 2035, the government has
OL,10,Festimated, as part of sweeping school
OL,11,Freforms.
OL,13,FThe proportion of children with SEND
OL,14,Fon the current highest level of
OL,15,Fsupport in school is projected to
OL,16,Fstart falling each year from the end
OL,17,Fof the decade.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FWhile the percentage of pupils with an
OL,7,FEHCP is predicted to keep rising until
OL,8,F2029/30, the government has estimated
OL,9,Fit will drop to around 4.7% by 2034/35
OL,10,Ffrom 5.8% currently.
OL,12,FChildren in year three or above
OL,13,Fcurrently will keep their EHCP until
OL,14,Fat least age 16, and those in year two
OL,15,For below will be reassessed when they
OL,16,Ftransition to year seven.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FThe policy documents propose a new
OL,7,Fplan with legal footing for all
OL,8,Fchildren with SEND called individual
OL,9,Fsupport plans (ISPs), which have
OL,10,Fmultiple tiers of support ` targeted
OL,11,Fand targeted plus. Children will not
OL,12,Fneed to have a diagnosis to access
OL,13,Fthese.
OL,15,FChildren with the most complex needs
OL,16,Fwill still have EHCPs, which will
OL,17,Funderpin new specialist provision
OL,18,Fpackages.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/22
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43120
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1771868901
OL,3,CParents 'forced to remortgage house'
OL,4,Camid battle for son's SEND provision
OL,6,FAssessments for the new system, which
OL,7,Fwill be consulted on for 12 weeks,
OL,8,Fwill start in September 2029 with no
OL,9,Fchanges to current support before "at
OL,10,Fleast September 2030".
OL,12,FWhen the new legislation comes into
OL,13,Feffect, children with EHCPs will be
OL,14,Freassessed at the end of their
OL,15,Feducation phase and it will be decided
OL,16,Fwhether they need a specialist
OL,17,Fprovision package. If they do, a new
OL,18,FEHCP will be developed.
OL,26,@qD@cOUrD@UO]
